{
  "stem": "2906.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In Stalingrad, they put us in the horse-- in horse and carriages to a kolkhoz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "A kolkhoz is a village that is a Communist.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Everything goes together.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well, the whole thing was Communist, everything together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But this village we came there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In there, they gave us, like-- some people took in the-- the people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Three.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But these-- these families took three, this three-- the Russian families took in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I, and my brother, and my girlfriend, they gave us a little shed that we stayed, like, private.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And everybody had to go and work in the fields, because they took all the soldiers, they took away everybody.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They need people to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is everything from the government.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They tell you to go there, that give you the horse and [?carriage?], and they take these people that-- Whatever they do is from the government.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You don't do nothing by yourself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I told-- I knew how to sew, and I told-- there was a-- a-- the president from the-- from the thing and his wife, and I told her, I know how to sew.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she invited me--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was-- they used to call him [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Presidatzer. ?] He was the president from the village.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I told his wife that I know how to sew dresses.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So she invite me, and I was working by her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And every night, they didn't give me money, but they gave me milk, and they gave cheese.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I used to bring to my place, and all our friends used to come every evening and eat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All day.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they were very nice people, I thought.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't know if we were Jewish or not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't ask us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't tell them.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
